# Anchor to repo root — `data/` (unanchored) accidentally swallowed
# scripts/data/* source code. Keep the repo-root data/ folder ignored
# (working data, scraped dumps, transcript caches) without affecting
# nested data/ directories elsewhere in the tree.
/data/

